<p align="center">
  <b>FastOpenAPI</b> is a library for generating and integrating OpenAPI schemas using Pydantic and various frameworks.
</p>

<p align="center">
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/github/license/mr-fatalyst/fastopenapi">
